Hi, I need an API access token please

To fetch your API Access Token, please log in to the Newsbreak Admanager Platform. Once logged in, click on Tools - Resources - Request Your Token. After your request is approved, you will receive an API key which you can use to authenticate your API requests. For more detailed instructions, you can refer to our [API Integration Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/26530008151309-Introduction-to-App-Install-Events). If you have any issues or need further assistance, feel free to contact our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com.
